modShortDescription: Another classic bigger backpack mod. This 7 Days to Die mod increases the backpack slots to 50.
modDescription:
Another classic bigger backpack mod. This 7 Days to Die mod increases the [backpack](https://7daystodiemods.com/tag/7-days-to-die-backpack/) slots to 50.

**[Download](https://botmanhosting.com/A18/HH_50_Slot_Backpack.zip)**

The forum topic of the mod is [here](https://community.7daystodie.com/topic/11963-highopes-modlets/).
